==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Љ''', '''љ''' (''italics: Љ, љ'')

#The fourteenth letter of the Serbian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is '''љ''' (lj) and it has no equivalent in English. It is pronounced by combining the sounds ''l'' and ''y''. It is similar to the Spanish ''ll''. It is preceded by [[л|Л]] and followed by [[м|М]].

